But it is n't all head banging and hot chocolate for these boys , they still have to go to school and do their homework .

They say they do n't love the classroom but go because ` it 's important ' . But all three love science and social studies , because it 's ` like a comic book with all those wars and fights ' .

What 's their advice for younger musicians struggling to make it in the dog-eat-dog world of heavy metal ?

` Believe in your dreams , ' says Jarad . ` Hard work pays off . '

Adds Alec : ` Follow your heart ' .

